OL,3,CHealth and social care services face
OL,4,Crecord #58 deficit
OL,6,FA record-high deficit has been
OL,7,Fforecast for health and social care
OL,8,Fservices in the south west of Scotland.
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway's Integration
OL,11,FJoint Board (IJB) has been warned a
OL,12,F#58m deficit is forecast for 2025/26,
OL,13,Fand savings of more than #30m need to
OL,14,Fbe found.
