OL,3,CHealth and social care services face
OL,4,Crecord #58 deficit
OL,6,FA meeting heard how the accounts for
OL,7,Fthe previous year were only balanced
OL,8,Fdue to extra funding from the Health
OL,9,Fand Social Care Partnership's
OL,10,Fstatutory partners. That included
OL,11,F#22.6m extra from the NHS and #1.8m
OL,12,Ffrom the Council.
OL,14,FChief Officer Gareth Marr said: "Our
OL,15,Fstaff and communities continue to show
OL,16,Fremarkable resilience, but the
OL,17,Fpressures on health and social care
OL,18,Fare mounting.
