OL,3,CHealth and social care services face
OL,4,Crecord #58 deficit
OL,6,F"Without urgent renewal, we will
OL,7,Fstruggle to keep pace with the needs
OL,8,Fof local people."
OL,10,FReserves for last year also fell by
OL,11,Fmore than half from #8.8m to #4.1m.
OL,13,F"We are not just facing a financial
OL,14,Fgap - we are facing a fundamental test
OL,15,Fof how we deliver care. Transformation
OL,16,Fis not optional; it's essential," Mr
OL,17,FMarr, said.
