OL,6,FHe added: "Our priority remains the
OL,7,Fsame ` safe, effective, compassionate
OL,8,Fcare for local people - but we must
OL,9,Fdeliver it in new ways or otherwise
OL,10,Frisk letting down those who need us
OL,11,Fmost."
OL,13,FThe meeting was told how the pressures
OL,14,Fare being mirrored in services across
OL,15,Fthe region, with demand for emergency
OL,16,Fcare rising, hospital discharges being
OL,17,Fdelayed and waiting lists for planned
OL,18,Ftreatments growing.
